01:48.609 --> 01:53.114
I'm good. A little busy.
A lot of stuff going on.

01:53.197 --> 01:56.700
Out for a jog? Well, why not.

02:19.348 --> 02:23.394
Does that guy look familiar?
- Congratulations on the new album.

02:23.477 --> 02:27.857
Well done, Tuomas.
- Are you wearing long johns?

02:43.998 --> 02:47.543
