are coming soon.

03:24.538 --> 03:29.376
Guess who's coming to
Tuomas' bachelor party? Willy.

03:29.460 --> 03:34.506
Willy? Oh, Willy Kallonen!
Really?

03:34.590 --> 03:38.510
Yes. He promised to bring along
some strippers.

03:38.594 --> 03:41.847
No one does that anymore, do they?

03:42.723 --> 03:45.309
More than one stripper?
- He's loaded.

03:45.392 --> 03:50.147
Wait a second.
I want my best friends to hear this.

03:50.272 --> 03:53.442
Mirkku, shoot.

03:55.444 --> 03:59.949
Not one good review?
Or even mediocre?

04:00.658 --> 04:07.414
But hey... You're getting married.
Focus on that.

04:08.415 --> 04:10.960
Pull strength from that.

04:11.043 --> 04:13.295
Right?

04:24.014 --> 04:27.518
Tuomas Lilja - the musical equivalent
of haemorrhoids

04:42.324 --> 04:45.577
Niklas, you have a visitor!
- What?

04:46.704 --> 04:50.541
Antti.
- How do I look?

04:50.624 --> 04:54.295
I have that date.
-Jaana, I'll take it from here.

04:54.378 --> 04:58.841
No, I asked her to stay.
I need a female perspective.

05:04.596 --> 05:10.728
Hi, I'm Antti Kulmala, a 38-year-old
bachelor from Southern Finland.

05:10.811 --> 05:13.605
Well? -Why do you talk
like a beauty queen?

05:13.689 --> 05:16.483
Don't you have nametags?
- On a date?

05:16.567 --> 05:22.364
It's a speed date. 40 women,
three minutes each. Nippe told me.

05:24.908 --> 05:28.412
Well? Is this over the top?

05:28.495 --> 05:34.001
How can that be over the top?
What do you normally wear?

05:34.084 --> 05:36.754
My orange T-shirt.

05:39.089 --> 05:43.052
That's perfect. You're ready.

05:43.135 --> 05:48.015
What time does it start?
- It isn't until tomorrow.

05:48.098 --> 05:51.268
I'm not an idiot.
- Okay. Good luck.

05:51.393 --> 05:54.938
You're bleeding.
Did you use the shaver again?

05:55.022 --> 05:58.609
Goddammit.
- Are you okay?

05:58.692 --> 06:02.404
Seeing blood makes me
feel dizzy these days.

06:02.488 --> 06:05.657
It's an age thing.
- Thanks.

06:05.741 --> 06:10.037
I feel like I don't know you anymore.

06:11.455 --> 06:15.459
It was just a magazine article
from long ago.

06:15.542 --> 06:18.504
I helped Antti out.

06:18.587 --> 06:23.384
Niklas... I want to
tell you something.

06:23.467 --> 06:28.389
But I need you to focus.
- Look, that's Willy Kallonen.

06:28.472 --> 06:32.476
I used to know him.
How did he get tickets?

06:32.559 --> 06:37.481
How should I know?
- He may come to the bachelor party.

06:37.564 --> 06:39.983
If he's still alive by then.

06:40.067 --> 06:42.861
I couldn't tell him.

06:45.781 --> 06:50.536
It isn’t just that. No!

06:52.830 --> 06:55.207
I have to go. Bye.

07:06.885 --> 07:10.222
I have that...

07:15.519 --> 07:19.481
Here comes the gong!

07:20.065 --> 07:23.986
How many times a day... a week
should a man go to the gym?

07:24.069 --> 07:27.739
As many times as he likes.
- What would be good for me?

07:27.823 --> 07:32.828
Take your paper, your pen,
and your drink with you.

07:32.911 --> 07:37.791
Hi. I'm Antti. Antti Kulmala.

07:37.875 --> 07:41.753
This is my first time here.
Hopefully not the last.

07:41.837 --> 07:46.049
Or actually, it would be better
if this was the last time.

07:46.592 --> 07:49.887
One guinea pig was left
in the microwave oven...

07:49.970 --> 07:54.308
They're kind of cute.
Stegosaurus, mainly.

07:54.391 --> 07:56.268
Do you like dinosaurs?

07:56.351 --> 08:03.192
Do you like dogs? -Yeah.
I took a class on dog trimming.

08:03.525 --> 08:08.363
Your name is Inka? Do you come
from an Indian background?

08:09.948 --> 08:12.993
No? -Here comes the gong!

08:13.076 --> 08:18.207
You're beautiful as you are,
but an Indian...

08:18.290 --> 08:20.083
Inka. Indian.

08:26.423 --> 08:28.550
Excuse me.

08:29.635 --> 08:32.929
There must've been a mistake.

08:33.013 --> 08:36.099
No one ticked my box.
- That happens.

08:36.183 --> 08:39.520
Come again next Saturday.
I'll give you a discount.

08:39.602 --> 08:42.063
What?

08:42.981 --> 08:48.362
There were over 30 single women,
and no one wants to see me again?

08:48.445 --> 08:52.533
Yeah. -I was brushed off 30 times!

08:52.616 --> 08:54.618
I'm sorry.

09:04.211 --> 09:06.713
One more thing.

09:06.797 --> 09:11.718
You have the contact details
for all the women.

09:12.719 --> 09:17.558
Hypothetically,
how much would they cost?

09:18.392 --> 09:21.395
I can't break that trust.

09:21.895 --> 09:25.107
I have to know what's wrong with me.

09:26.191 --> 09:29.111
I can tell you that for free.

09:33.824 --> 09:37.202
You did what?
- I stole them.

09:37.286 --> 09:41.832
Have you called the women?
-just three so far.

09:41.915 --> 09:45.252
I pretended to be a telemarketer.
- What did they say?

09:45.335 --> 09:49.423
They didn't buy anything.
One subscribed to a newspaper.

09:53.010 --> 09:57.055
What's up, shitfaces?
Want to get plastered? -Willy!

09:57.139 --> 10:00.892
Great to see you!
What an awesome car!

10:00.976 --> 10:05.147
Well... It's nice.
Listen, Willy... or Henrik...

10:05.230 --> 10:10.277
Why don't you park on the
marked spot? It was in the e-mail.

10:10.360 --> 10:14.948
Good old Nippe,
always nit-picking.

10:15.407 --> 10:18.285
Nippe! Stop nit-picking.

10:18.368 --> 10:23.206
But still... Do you have
a pink shirt as agreed? -No.

10:23.290 --> 10:26.251
Does the driver speak Finnish?

10:26.835 --> 10:31.006
Can you please drive this car
to the marketplace?

10:31.089 --> 10:34.343
The marked place.
- I'll take care of it. Björn!

10:39.014 --> 10:41.725
This way.
- Willy is such a cool guy.

10:41.808 --> 10:46.063
He could've gone anywhere,
but he wanted to come here.

10:46.146 --> 10:50.651
Enough with the raving.
- You're just jealous.

10:50.734 --> 10:53.487
Of him? Why?
- He's got everything.

10:53.570 --> 10:57.949
At that rate, he won't live
to see 40. -At least he's lived.

10:58.033 --> 11:01.244
And I haven't?
- Hush, they're coming.

11:02.120 --> 11:08.001
Can't we talk about this? -You've
been yelling at me about the rings!

11:08.085 --> 11:12.839
You didn't even look at them!
- You haven't listened to my album.

11:12.923 --> 11:16.551
Stop going on about that.
- Let me look at them!

11:18.804 --> 11:22.265
Wow. They're fabulous,
and probably expensive.

11:22.349 --> 11:25.936
How do we pay for them
when my album doesn't sell?

11:26.019 --> 11:30.315
Should we call this off?
- Yeah, we'll come back later.

11:30.399 --> 11:32.984
I've had a load of shit dumped on me!

11:33.068 --> 11:37.072
You don't know what it feels like
to read those reviews.

11:37.155 --> 11:41.118
Why do you read them then?
- It's part of my job!

11:41.201 --> 11:46.373
And one more thing. If I ever get
positive feedback again -

11:46.456 --> 11:51.002
I'd like it to be from someone
who's listened to the album!

11:51.086 --> 11:55.632
Abort!
-just tell the truth!

11:55.757 --> 11:59.177
Truth? That sounds strange
coming from your mouth.

11:59.261 --> 12:03.890
Here we go!
- Do you even love me anymore?

12:03.974 --> 12:05.934
Of course.
- Then show it!

12:06.017 --> 12:09.730
Am I not trying? -You don't think
of anyone but yourself!

12:09.813 --> 12:14.526
I actually thought that
you wanted to change! Tuomas!

12:18.196 --> 12:21.324
Surprise!

12:21.408 --> 12:25.829
Tuomas is supposed to have a bachelor
party, but we can come back...

12:25.912 --> 12:30.083
Willy! Unbelievable!

12:32.794 --> 12:36.631
Go. We can fight later.

13:27.557 --> 13:33.522
Hell... I've missed you.
- I've missed you, too.

13:33.605 --> 13:37.234
Why are you sulking?
That's no way to get married.

13:38.193 --> 13:42.697
I know what will help.
- I'm not doing that.

13:42.823 --> 13:46.952
And neither should you.
- But you dare to get married.

14:06.096 --> 14:11.309
Are you okay?
- Hey, which of us is sulking?

14:12.853 --> 14:15.146
Look at this bird.

14:15.981 --> 14:18.441
Who's that?
- Is she single?

14:18.525 --> 14:23.488
Miss G, Carola Hahlqvist.
- Why does her name sound familiar?

14:23.572 --> 14:25.740
She's the biggest buyer in Finland.

14:25.866 --> 14:29.411
If she distributed your album,
you'd get a gold record.

14:29.494 --> 14:33.039
She's not single.
Is she single?

14:35.208 --> 14:39.880
Could she really do it? -Remember
that triple platinum Christmas album?

14:39.963 --> 14:46.803
Was that her doing?
- This lady likes her toys big.

14:47.429 --> 14:50.765
Hey, Tuomas is getting married.

14:52.601 --> 14:55.562
Yeah.

14:56.104 --> 14:59.316
I was just trying to help.

15:05.655 --> 15:10.702
What? -If you're not going for
Miss G, can I...

15:10.785 --> 15:12.746
Be my guest.

15:22.255 --> 15:25.425
Nippe...

15:26.217 --> 15:30.013
Thanks. -You weren't
offended earlier, were you?

15:30.430 --> 15:35.435
I was just kidding. You aren't always
nit-picking.<i> Comprendo, amigo?</i>

15:37.812 --> 15:40.607
<i>Hasta luego.</i>

15:40.982 --> 15:44.569
Don't talk bullshit.
- Okay.

15:46.655 --> 15:52.285
What you did was so wrong
and so inconsiderate, even for you.

15:55.080 --> 16:01.419
I know. What do you want me to say?
I'm sorry. Truly.

16:01.503 --> 16:04.089
You should apologise to Tuomas.

16:04.172 --> 16:09.761
He's actually thinking about fucking
your friend for triple platinum.

16:10.595 --> 16:15.016
Tuomas?
- Yeah. Have some decency.

16:15.100 --> 16:18.645
<i>Comprendo, amigo?
- Si.</i>

16:37.372 --> 16:42.794
Okay, I'll give it a try.
- Yes! Go, Tuomas!

16:46.256 --> 16:50.677
Shit, I thought that Nippe
knew about me and Jaana.

16:51.177 --> 16:55.348
What do you mean?
- That we've fucked.

16:55.432 --> 16:57.642
What?

16:58.685 --> 17:03.023
It was a long time ago,
but that doesn't make it okay.

17:03.106 --> 17:06.108
But I'll grab us some drinks.

17:07.527 --> 17:10.320
It was just a spare.

17:12.031 --> 17:18.288
Maybe I could lead Miss G to believe
that we could do something -

17:18.371 --> 17:20.540
but then nothing would happen.

17:20.623 --> 17:24.961
Has Willy fucked Jaana?
- There'd be nothing wrong with that.

17:25.086 --> 17:29.841
What did you say? -Willy told me
that he's fucked Jaana.

17:29.924 --> 17:33.803
No.
- Yes.

17:33.887 --> 17:37.891
What are we going to say
to Nippe? -Nothing.

17:37.974 --> 17:40.810
Nothing?
- Willy is our friend.

17:40.894 --> 17:44.606
And Nippe isn't?
- What am I not?

17:45.732 --> 17:49.235
Nothing. You're not finished
with your beer.

17:49.319 --> 17:52.405
Willy has fucked Jaana.

18:18.181 --> 18:20.350
He left in style.

18:20.433 --> 18:24.938
Did someone take off
his bowling shoes?

18:25.021 --> 18:29.609
People tend to walk out in them.
- This one won't.

18:39.577 --> 18:42.831
Niklas...
- Don't.

18:42.914 --> 18:46.584
We have to talk about it.

18:47.752 --> 18:50.463
Okay, I made a mistake.

18:50.547 --> 18:53.800
No. A mistake is forgetting
your keys inside the car -

18:53.883 --> 18:56.594
or getting Grandma's pills mixed up.

18:56.678 --> 19:01.224
But hiding the sausage of a
childhood friend on a seminar trip -

19:01.307 --> 19:03.059
is not a mistake.

19:03.184 --> 19:06.980
Why don't you go to the funeral?
You knew him better than I did.

19:08.439 --> 19:13.528
Hi, honey. What did you hear
Mummy and Daddy say?

19:13.611 --> 19:15.905
Like from the beginning?

19:34.591 --> 19:37.010
Don't ask. just drive.

19:49.314 --> 19:52.483
Hey... I know what
you're going through.

19:53.985 --> 19:56.988
The same thing happened to me.

19:57.906 --> 20:01.034
Except that the guy didn't die.

20:01.117 --> 20:05.413
But how many men are so lucky -

20:05.496 --> 20:10.293
that just when someone
has fucked their wife, he dies?

20:11.794 --> 20:15.340
They probably
wouldn't be pall-bearers.

20:15.423 --> 20:18.301
You can thank Malena for that.
- Who?

20:18.384 --> 20:21.471
Willy's wife. Didn't you know?

20:21.554 --> 20:24.974
How should I have known?
I barely knew the guy.

20:25.058 --> 20:30.605
She asked me first,
but my lower back has been acting up.

20:31.356 --> 20:34.984
I can't risk spraining it.
- Where's Tuomas?

20:35.068 --> 20:37.737
He's not coming.
- Not coming?

20:37.820 --> 20:40.698
I'm not coming.
- I told you so.

20:40.782 --> 20:43.826
I'm getting married tomorrow.
- It's not that.

20:43.910 --> 20:47.163
He was asked to perform,
just like at our wedding.

20:47.288 --> 20:52.001
But now he can't do either
because he's lost his voice. -I have!

20:52.085 --> 20:54.545
Tuomas... Even Nippe is coming -

20:54.629 --> 20:58.549
and Willy fucked his wife
with that enormous dick. -What?

20:58.633 --> 21:01.594
Just a figure of speech.

21:01.678 --> 21:07.767
You've been invited to a funeral,
and you can't refuse.

21:11.729 --> 21:14.565
Okay then. But I won't sing.

21:19.195 --> 21:22.907
We'll bring him back on time.
I promise.

21:23.908 --> 21:28.579
Don't worry. We'll persuade him
to sing. We'll cheer him up.

21:28.663 --> 21:31.958
On our way to a funeral?

21:34.002 --> 21:36.421
Where are we?

21:48.182 --> 21:51.769
You've taken good care of your car.

21:51.853 --> 21:57.692
Mum washed it this morning.
- No wonder this seat is wet.

21:57.775 --> 22:00.737
Same here.
Why didn't you go to a car wash?

22:00.820 --> 22:03.948
Mum does it for free.

22:05.867 --> 22:08.995
Do you think Willy will be
cremated or buried?

22:09.078 --> 22:13.916
He seared himself on a sauna stove
as a kid. I bet he'll be buried.

22:16.169 --> 22:21.549
Where did the nickname Willy
come from? Guys?

22:24.677 --> 22:27.764
Guess what I brought along?

22:32.935 --> 22:36.022
Tuomas doesn't want that right now.

22:36.105 --> 22:40.693
The record company said that
this is the best inner sleeve ever.

22:40.777 --> 22:45.740
Check out these colours.
A beautiful picture.

22:51.788 --> 22:54.791
What the fuck?
Is this already on sale?

22:54.874 --> 22:58.836
Nice going, Antti.
- Hey... Okay. Give it to me.

22:58.920 --> 23:01.839
Let's forget about this.

23:08.513 --> 23:11.641
What? Did it hit something? -No.

23:11.724 --> 23:14.102
Pull over.

23:22.735 --> 23:27.907
I can see the headlines. "Lilja's
album is even endangering traffic."

23:27.990 --> 23:30.701
Antti will take care of this.

23:30.785 --> 23:32.912
Oh my...

23:37.291 --> 23:40.086
Hi.

23:43.047 --> 23:44.799
Or not.

23:48.553 --> 23:54.100
You and your shitty album! -This
isn't the album's fault, but Antti's!

23:56.602 --> 24:02.358
Oh my God. I'm going to die,
and Jaana thinks I don't love her.

24:04.068 --> 24:06.237
What's going on?

24:11.242 --> 24:13.077
Bye.

24:25.298 --> 24:28.551
How did it go? -just fine.

24:29.719 --> 24:32.305
Did they let us go?
- Yeah. Sure.

24:32.597 --> 24:37.310
Antti Kulmala,
ladies and gentlemen! Hats off!

24:40.146 --> 24:45.401
Well, what did you say to them?
- I told them it was an accident.

24:45.526 --> 24:49.989
Was that enough?
- No, it wasn't.

24:50.072 --> 24:54.577
I know that those guys
won't settle for an apology.

24:54.660 --> 24:59.123
What did you promise them?
Not my gig, I hope?

24:59.832 --> 25:01.667
Well...

25:03.294 --> 25:09.842
The thing is that...
you need to act a little.

25:09.926 --> 25:12.678
Me? Act what?

25:14.180 --> 25:18.142
That you're a war veteran
from Afghanistan.

25:20.394 --> 25:24.440
What... A war veteran?

25:24.565 --> 25:27.902
We're going to their club.
It's near here.

25:27.985 --> 25:33.157
You got us invited to their club?
Are you crazy?

25:33.241 --> 25:38.955
I froze. You know me.
When I panic, I'll say anything.

25:39.038 --> 25:41.791
I thought they were going to kill me.

25:45.586 --> 25:50.341
We're taking our friend to a funeral.

25:51.050 --> 25:55.972
He's a war veteran. From Afghanistan.

25:56.055 --> 25:59.684
Like a peacekeeper, you mean?
- Something like that.

25:59.767 --> 26:03.229
I'm a clerk!
- There's something else.

26:07.692 --> 26:12.446
I may have said
that you're a little...

26:12.738 --> 26:14.490
A little what, Antti?

26:16.742 --> 26:21.372
Disabled?
- No! Of course not.

26:21.455 --> 26:26.877
Injured.
- Injured? How?

26:26.961 --> 26:30.715
I can't remember.
I completely blacked out.

26:31.173 --> 26:33.342
You can't remember?

26:34.885 --> 26:40.099
But they want to show their guns
to the war veteran.

26:40.391 --> 26:44.145
Fuck, we're going to die.
- Nonsense.

26:44.228 --> 26:50.818
I have to know my goddamn injuries!
- You'll think of something.

26:50.901 --> 26:54.280
Get in, guys.

27:22.183 --> 27:24.852
This game is shit.

27:28.356 --> 27:31.734
The drinks are free.

27:31.817 --> 27:37.281
These guys are chilled out.
- Really? Look at their dartboard.

27:37.990 --> 27:40.868
It has my face on it.

27:40.951 --> 27:46.290
Maybe they don't like you
until they get to know you.

27:47.541 --> 27:52.213
Those girls are strippers,
by the way. Quite a coincidence.

27:52.296 --> 27:55.925
Look at those jugs.
My mum's were like those.

27:56.884 --> 28:00.429
Maybe we could have
your bachelor party here. Cool!

28:00.513 --> 28:04.308
Let's have a proper party.
- Come here.

28:04.392 --> 28:07.812
Thank your new friends,
and we'll walk out of here.

28:07.895 --> 28:11.524
Nod if you understand.
- We can't.

28:12.191 --> 28:15.319
The boss wants to meet us. -Who?

28:15.403 --> 28:18.948
He takes war veterans
very seriously.

28:23.577 --> 28:26.080
Here are the gentlemen.

28:28.124 --> 28:30.876
What's your name, veteran?

28:33.879 --> 28:36.173
Huh?

28:39.051 --> 28:41.387
Pekka.

28:41.637 --> 28:47.184
He told us that Pekka is
very interested in our guns.

28:48.102 --> 28:51.480
Guns?

